  <prompt>
    Implement the Dialog API authentication fallback for older Outlook clients that
    don't support NAA. Use Office.context.ui.displayDialogAsync to open an auth popup
    and handle the OAuth callback.
  </prompt>

  <role>
    Frontend developer specializing in Office Add-in authentication. Expert in
    Office Dialog API and cross-window communication.
  </role>

  <goal>
    A working DialogAuthService that authenticates users in older clients using
    the Office Dialog API with proper callback handling.
  </goal>

  <context>
    <background>
      Some older Outlook clients don't support NAA. The Dialog API provides a fallback
      by opening a dialog window for authentication. The add-in must handle the OAuth
      callback and extract the token from the dialog.
    </background>
    <relevant-files>
      <file>src/client/office-addins/shared/auth/DialogAuthService.ts (to create)</file>
